news: The competition locations in Frederiksberg (Denmark) and Skopje (North Macedonia) have been cancelled as well.
The competition location in Sofia (Bulgaria) and Bełżyce (Poland) has been cancelled because of the COVID-19 outbreak.

The competition locations in Czech Republic (Červený Kostelec) and Italy (Milano and Monterotondo) have been cancelled because of the coronavirus outbreak and the resulting measures by the government. All registered competitors should have received an email.
